The '''Center on Organizational Innovation''' ('''COI''') is a research center at [[Columbia University]]'s [[Institute for Social and Economic Research and Policy]]. The center, established in 2000 and directed by sociologist [[David C. Stark|David Stark]], promotes research in the areas of [[organizational studies]], [[science and technology studies]] and [[economic sociology]], with an emphasis on [[innovation]] and [[Reflexivity_(social_theory)|reflexivity]].{{Ref|Stark-COI}}

